items: New 'Compact View' feature. Global level in View menu. Job level in context menu for Job. Ability level in context menu for Ability
New What's New window
New 'Show Abilities Availability Map' under View menu. Show if one or more abilities can be used between two other usages of same ability
Fixed garbage boss attacks when importing from FFLogs after patch 4.4
Anticipation added to tank abilities
Removed Dependency on XIVDB tooltips. New tooltips implementation is in-progress
Red Mage abilities
Upgrade to Angular 7
Now we save Filters, View and Hidden abilities when you save fight and restore on load
Time in boss attack dialog
Copy/paste of boss attacks. Yeah.
Side panel on items select. Still thinking what to show there. Any ideas?
New Restore Hidden sub menu in job context menu to return visibility to specific hidden ability instead of restore them all
Checkboxes for pets and compact view in job context menu
Export to google sheets deprecated
Sacred Soil for scholar
New Tools menu
Sticky Attacks tool. When tool is on and you move boss attack, all boss attacks with time more than selected will be moved accordingly
Export to Google Sheets is back
Time in Boos Attack dialog can be adjusted with mouse wheel. Just mouse wheel: +/- 1 second, Ctrl+mouse wheel: +/- 1 minute
Small fixes
Update to Ability Availability. Updated color to be not that 'blood from eyes'. Now shows exact area where ability can be used.
Update to table view: improved abilities layout.
Updated FFLogsImport dialog
Improved loading time from FFLogs, Should be ~10 times faster.
Fixed stances loading.
New home page. Tell me what you think.
Now Job's collapsed/expanded state saves when you save fight.
Jobs are sorted by (tank, heal, dd) during Import from FFLogs. Probably exact order should be extracted to Settings. Also, looking into the way to change order of jobs manually.
Help dialog a bit changed, but still in progress.
Fixed importing of few abilities
First setting in Settings: Boss Attacks Source (Cast, Damage).
Second setting in Settings: Jobs sort order after import by Tank, heal, dd can be configured now.
Minor fixes and improvements
New settings for Default Filter and View. These settings as applied when you start new or import data from FFLogs.
Updates to team work feature: notifications of new comrades (dis)connected. List of connected in toolbar with live updates.
New tab in settings: Teamwork. You can setup your Display Name to be used in teamwork.
Few fixes related to game patches.
New abilities for healers
Sidepanel implementation. Can show additional info about selection in side panel area with different actions. If you have any ideas, contact me in Discord
Internal improvements.
New boss attacks filters by damage type.
We moved to ng-zorro UI framework.
Added additional filters: Enmity.
Some improvements for tablest. I am testing on my IPad pro.
Bug fixes
Job changes for 5.0
5.05 updates
FFLogs integration fix
TeamWork is deprecated now and integrated into editor by default. You can now share link of saved project and openning of this link automatically enables TeamWork.
Small fixes
Dancer new abilities
Added support for fractions in SWTOR. Now need info for Republic classes and abilities
Fixed duration on medicine. Pull request from Makar8000.
Added Colorful Durations in View menu. Designed to show type of ability duration with color and better identify it
If you do not like my colors, open Settings and set colors you like more.
Fixed medicine import from fflogs
Fixed filters
Updates to some actions
Fixed import from Boss Templates. Now you can import fight from fflogs and then import predefined boss attacks from Boss Templates menu
Now you can setup your ingame character in Settings/FFLogs. After character is configured system will show your latest parses in 'Import from FFLogs' dialog.
5.1 changes
Fixed 'Import from FFLogs' dialog did not recognize links without enounter id
Upgrade to the latest versions of Angular, NG-ZORRO and Vis. Some issues are possible.
Completely removed context menus. Actions are available in side panel. Job, Job Abilities and Downtimes are now selectable.
Tags for Boss Attack. One can assign custom tags to Boss Attack
Source for Boss Attack. You can assign source of attack to Boss Attack
Brand new Filter menu with support for filtering Boss Attacks by Tags and Source
Side panel for Boss Attack now shows Available Defensive Abilities
New menu Item 'Open as Table'. Opens current fight as table view with predefined templates.
Ma-a-any small fixes
Small rework of Recent Activities on home page: added pin and remove actions to list
Copy & Paste for multiple attacks
Fixed issues with reopening URLs for created and inported from FFLogs timelines
Fixed Time column filter in table view
Fixed sort order of recent activities on Home screen
Table view now indicates target of abilities.
Fixed collapsed job expand icon
Table view now shows relative time of ability usage for Defensive table.
Preliminary implementation of Mitigation information for boss attack. It shows calculated values for mitigation and shields.
Small style fixes
Now we save and restore `filters, view options` for each fight you view or edit. Custom view presets is next step.
New sidebar area for Buff abilities: 'Covered OGCDs'. Shows, yep, dmage OGCDs covered by this buff.
Few UI improvemets for sidebar.
